a measurement or indication

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:40.880
of how volatile, or what's the
standard deviation of a price

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:43.080
can change over time.

00:07:43.080 --> 00:07:44.830
That's all you need
to know right now.

00:07:44.830 --> 00:07:47.480
I'm not going to ask
you questions later.

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:52.737
So my desk quant
look at me, said--

00:07:52.737 --> 00:07:54.320
this is supposed to
be options trading

00:07:54.320 --> 00:07:58.120
desk, so he look at me puzzled.

00:07:58.120 --> 00:08:00.020
So instead of
answering my question,

00:08:00.020 --> 00:08:02.780
